  "instructions": [
    "preheat oven to 375 f.",
    "roll out the dough and place it in a 9-inch tart pan with a removable bottom.",
    "cook the onions until caramelized, then set aside.",
    "whisk together the eggs, heavy cream, and a pinch of salt and pepper.",
    "add the grated cheese, chopped green onions, and sesame seeds to the egg mixture and stir to combine.",
    "pour the egg mixture into the tart shell and top with the caramelized onions and a drizzle of gochujang-glazed jelly.",
    "bake the quiche for 35-40 minutes, or until set and golden brown.",
    "poach the eggs and place them on top of the quiche before serving.",
    "bake for an additional 2-3 minutes to melt the cheese and set the eggs."
  ],
